Install
=======

This is the basic version:

    $ ./checkout.sh      # Download
    $ ./setup.sh         # Install & test        


Dependencies for EPD 7-1
-------------------------

Necessary packages to install for EPD:

    easy_install pip
    pip install virtualenv
    
    
Run
=============


Try this:

    fly_behaviors_simulations --fast -T 2    
    
Or if you have mplayer/mencoder installed, you can also create a video:

    fly_behaviors_simulations --fast -T 2 --video